recent_decisions.decision:
Profile gossip now verifies Ed25519 signatures when present (`should_accept_profile_gossip` in src/relay/handlers/federation.rs). Empty signatures still admitted under trust-by-source — clients don't sign profiles yet. Once they do, this gate flips to a hard reject for unsigned profiles. Canonical signing format is `profile_v1
{public_key}
{name}
...
{timestamp}`. 8 unit tests added.
